 ghee, please refer to the recipes on this recipe chip.","Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook <\/em>or <em>Everyday Cookbook<\/em> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","You can store this paste in the refrigerator for up to 5 days or in the freezer, in a freezable container, for up to 1 month.","Use as a base for curries or stir-fries. Or use it in place of the Tandoori paste in the Masala bread rolls (please refer to the recipe on this recipe chip)."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","1 total recipe"]}